creator: DEAR Health Inc
descriptionHtml:
DEARhealth is a new solution enabling you securely manage your health. Use your DEARhealth account to manage your health and disease activity under the principles of Value-Based healthcare.

We measure the value of your care with a Value Quotient® or VQ® which captures the value of healthcare services to individual patients, including disease control, quality of life and daily productivity.

DEARhealth allows you to:
• Check your current and historical VQ®
• View your individualized Care Program
• Complete your home care
• Contact your healthcare team via secure messaging
• View upcoming labs, clinic visits, scheduled home care, and procedures
• Learn about your disease with MyAcademy
• Access your Wellness programs - MyCoach, MyMenu, MyAccupressure, My Fitness, MyYoga and MyMeditation.
• Review and confirm your medication

To access the DEARhealth services delivered through the app, you must create an account with your healthcare provider. Visit DEARhealth website for a listing of supported providers. If your provider is not listed or you need help setting up the account, please contact them directly.

For feedback about the app, contact us at support@dearhealth.com
descriptionShort: DEARhealth is a new solution enabling you securely manage your health.
